{"tid":2111884,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"艾利臣：衝100分紀錄不是利物浦的目標","createTime":"2020-07-17T01:33:47.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-17T11:53:11.000Z","uid":67225,"like":13,"dislike":22,"uniUserReply":28,"replies":[{"pid":"2e6716b00348305a47ee5ada487daf91dc661d74","tid":2111884,"uid":67225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:33:47.000Z","msg":"利物浦已經鎖定英超冠軍，但隨著1：2不敵阿仙奴，亦即是今季「紅軍」最多可拿下的就是99分，未能成功衝擊曼城以往100分奪冠的英超紀錄。然而，門將艾利臣坦言不要緊。<br />\n<br />\n這位巴西球員說：「老實講，（分數紀錄）不是我們的目標，但當你開始想『我們可以打破紀錄』，破到很好，破不到的話也OK。最重要的目標是成為冠軍，我們做到了。沒有其他細微的事可以掩蓋成為冠軍這件事的光芒。」這一仗中，艾利臣及後防大將雲迪積克都有失誤，前者續說，他們都是常人，犯錯是難免的，重要的是可以從中學習，繼續努力。"},{"pid":"8b71fac38a3f213fc532aa61fdb9a0f8ff99fc1e","tid":2111884,"uid":67225,"like":26,"dislike":1,"score":25,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:34:19.000Z","msg":"平常心<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"36b72c6d3a8a9a1bcc4b7a18b5159d120568b634","tid":2111884,"uid":34468,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:34:21.000Z","msg":"平常心啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/abomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"709f6adcc5879ddae58405008f8a9b7b75c8cf40","tid":2111884,"uid":199893,"like":22,"dislike":0,"score":22,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:37:09.000Z","msg":"贏咗英超理撚得你"},{"pid":"a1dff2ab77b252e0dab092fe3bb58226d19dc066","tid":2111884,"uid":20809,"like":44,"dislike":36,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:38:55.000Z","msg":"咁唔該積返d陰德，對車果陣唔好搞事<br />\n死獌狗落歐霸對世界黎講最好"},{"pid":"78fb553caedcc77f8ce3dbd4c62d08c38e1b48aa","tid":2111884,"uid":63253,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:44:44.000Z","msg":"係時候出副選，比班正選抖抖<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5c5d195b368cc1086507604383414abc202de4ed","tid":2111884,"uid":181283,"like":8,"dislike":15,"score":-7,"quote":{"pid":"a1dff2ab77b252e0dab092fe3bb58226d19dc066","tid":2111884,"uid":20809,"like":44,"dislike":36,"score":8,"citedBy":4,"replyTime":"2020-07-17T01:38:55